le business beyond a certain point is counter productive since that leads t=
o a more responsibility and less time for other stuff.</p><p>A bootstrapped=
 business does still have growth as a primary goal and there is intention t=
o reach a larger size and complexity.</p><p>While I'm not sure that I like =
