vestment can be super helpful though. I like knowing how=E2=80=99s to get 2=
-10x value out of each dollar. It helps with growing fast. Current recessio=
n likely makes it easier for me to raise investment in some ways.</p><p>I s=
ometimes go out of my way to recommend everything but my own solution. It=
=E2=80=99s better when they connect the dots, and if they can=E2=80=99t.</p=
><p>Most B2B saas in time need a professional services division of some kin=
