s business done right does open doors.  Doing things that doesn=E2=80=99t s=
cale gets you access that doesn=E2=80=99t scale to the many.</p><p>I=E2=80=
=99ve recently come across an author by the name of April Dunford that made=
 my add value first and awesome approach fell a little less alone, and spec=
ial which is awesome. She is amazingly well written and spoken. Going to re=
ad more of her stuff in the next few months.</p><p>I accidentally closed a =
